{
  "texts": [
    "Experimental results on CIFAR-10/CIFAR-100, SVHN, and ImageNet demonstrate the effectiveness of this approach.",
    "26 proposed a graph pooling method based on self-attention.",
    "By combining graph convolution with self-attention, their method can simultaneously consider node features and graph topology.",
    "To ensure a fair comparison, they conducted experiments using the same training procedure and model architecture for existing pooling methods and their proposed method.",
    "The experimental results demonstrate that their method achieves superior graph classification performance on benchmark datasets with a reasonable number of parameters."
  ]
}